      • CHAMELEON_RUNTIME_MONITORING_PROPERTY

        public static final String CHAMELEON_RUNTIME_MONITORING_PROPERTY
        The property used to enable / disable the monitoring of the runtime directory. Monitoring means that new files will be handled, like a watch mode. The monitoring of the runtime directory is disabled by default.
        See Also:

        public static final String CHAMELEON_APPLICATION_MONITORING_PROPERTY
